was added.

Discussion: https://postgr.es/m/CAMbWs48Mmvm-acGevXuwpB=g5JMqVSL6i9z5UaJyLGJqa-XPAA@mail.gmail.com_|_Fix failure to detect some cases of improperly-nested aggregates.

