Discussion: https://postgr.es/m/CAMkU=1xTHkS6d0iptCWykHc1Xrh3LBic_gZDo3JzDYru815fLQ@mail.gmail.com_|_Prevent generating EEOP_AGG_STRICT_INPUT_CHECK operations when nargs == 0.

